txt.en: Dulglok is at Shrak Mauruk.\n\nYou should bring the chickens to Dulglok.

'Drop what you're doing and listen to me you filthy minion. The Men across the water have some plump and delicious chickens that just escaped their cages.\n\n'Go over there and steal them before those Gondorian pukes find out!'
Plump Hens the enemy is keeping escaped their cages and should be stolen before the enemy find out they're missing.
'Oh you've done well. Real well! I'd promote you but then who would be my favourite [placeholder] to yell at?!'
Escaped Chickens can be found roaming around Western Osgiliath.\n\nYou should steal the escaped chickens.
